subSubSection.paragraph:
Opisthosoma from dorsal side ovoid, with bristles and downy hairs, no marking on dorsal side. Four short spinnerets, apical segments of pls digitiform (
Fig. 2A, G
). Relative length of spinneret segments from base 23: 15: 23. Spigots small, number on each segment from base 8, 24, 21. Pms present, although small, spigots only distally. Aperture of booklungs are wide slits (
Fig. 2A
).

